{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/bss_gif-ezgif.com-speed.gif?t=1730068612\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CHANGE YOURSELF, CHANGE OTHERS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Burden Street Station is a non-linear narrative game set in a liminal train station about helping a cast of unusual creatures and spirits move on with their lives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect personality traits through talking and exploration, and wear them to unlock dialogue options and advance their stories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will come to know these spirits very well. You will learn a lot about them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Narrative gameplay system where character customisation is your dialogue options.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong> Stylish 2.5D analog art style.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong> 6 deep, detailed NPCs to explore.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>An unstable train station with randomly occurring events.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>An absolutely <i>insufferable</i> side-kick.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Almost entirely made by a single person.</strong></p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3126340?t=1730068612","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1730068612","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730068612","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730068612","categories":[{"description